## Expanding the Network

* Ubiquiti Mesh Dual-Band Access Point
* Ubiquiti Directional Dual-Band Antenna
* Ubiquiti EdgeRouter ERX-SFP
* Raspberry Pi
* Ethernet Cables 3' [3 per house]
* Ethernet Cables 10' [1 perhouse]
